{% endraw %}

Install

pip install co_py

Usage

{% raw %} 
from co_py.core import CFApi
{% endraw %}
Without api_key and secret
{% raw %} 
cf = CFApi()
{% endraw %}
With api_key and secret
{% raw %} 
import os
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
api_key = os.environ.get('API_KEY')
secret = os.environ.get('SECRET')
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
cf = CFApi(api_key=api_key, secret=secret)
{% endraw %}
